[A dramatic increase in cases of cholera is reported in Haiti and the Dominican Republic in 2015. Especially in Haiti, in the 5th year of the epidemic, seeing this upswing reflects the dramatic need for improved availability of safe water and a better sanitation system in this almost forgotten epidemic. - Mod.LL]
